title: Iron Maiden - Beast Over Palladium Live [Pre-FM ]1982ak32
description:
Iron Maiden - Beast Over Palladium Live[Pre-FM Master]1982ak320

This is an upgrade of the show previously shared as The Night Of The Living Dead from the concert Iron Maiden did at The Palladium, New York City on 29th June 1982.

Track List: (Artwork Included)
01 Murders In The Rue Morgue 
02 Wrathchild 
03 Run To The Hills 
04 Children Of The Damned 
05 The Number Of The Beast 
06 The Prisoner 
07 Hallowed Be Thy Name 
08 Phantom Of The Opera 
09 Iron Maiden 
10 Sanctuary 
11 Drifter

Credits
Bass, Vocals – Steve Harris
Drums – Clive Burr
Guitar – Adrian Smith  
Guitar –Dave Murray 
Lead Vocals – Bruce Dickinson
